      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row511563#s3",
      "text": "Per recent pulmonogy and    cardiology notes this shortness of breath has been getting gradually    worse."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row511563:4",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "He also notes a 40 lbs weight gain that he reports over the last    few weeks (f",
