      "source_ref": "note:row511563#s11",
      "text": "He    was given an ASA."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row511563:12",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Pressure dropped to 80s, then responded to 90s after    given some fluids (500cc",
